---
title: "applyAllowlistedWorkflowsUpdates (WorkflowRouter)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_role: onlyRole(DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE)
    q_check_role --> q_check_empty: caller is admin
    q_check_role --> q_revert_role: caller lacks admin role
    q_revert_role --> [*]: revert AccessControlUnauthorizedAccount()

    q_check_empty --> q_iter_removes: removes.length > 0 OR adds.length > 0
    q_check_empty --> q_revert_empty: removes.length == 0 AND adds.length == 0
    q_revert_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList()

    q_iter_removes --> q_remove_wf: i < removes.length
    q_iter_removes --> q_iter_adds: i >= removes.length (done)

    q_remove_wf --> q_remove_targets: workflowId = removes[i]
    q_remove_targets --> q_remove_id: _applyAllowlistedTargetsUpdates(workflowId, allTargets, empty)
    q_remove_id --> q_emit_remove: s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.remove(workflowId)
    q_emit_remove --> q_iter_removes: emit WorkflowIdRemovedFromAllowlist, i++

    q_iter_adds --> q_add_wf: i < adds.length
    q_iter_adds --> [*]: i >= adds.length (done)

    q_add_wf --> q_check_zero: workflowId = adds[i].workflowId
    q_check_zero --> q_add_id: workflowId != bytes32(0)
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: workflowId == bytes32(0)
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue()

    q_add_id --> q_add_targets: s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.add(workflowId)
    q_add_targets --> q_iter_adds: _applyAllowlistedTargetsUpdates(workflowId, empty, targetSelectors), i++

    note right of q_remove_wf
        INV-001: removing a workflowId first removes all its targets and selectors via _applyAllowlistedTargetsUpdates
        INV-002: s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.remove returns bool but result is not checked (silent no-op if already removed)
    end note

    note right of q_add_id
        INV-003: s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.add is idempotent (EnumerableSet), existing workflowId gets new targets appended
        INV-004: workflowId zero is rejected but no uniqueness check across adds array
    end note
